quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  56,75,"aqsm allah taealaa bmsaqt alnujum fi mgharbha fi alsma', wa'iinah laqasm law taelamun qadarh ezym"
  56,76,"aqsm allah taealaa bmsaqt alnujum fi mgharbha fi alsma', wa'iinah laqasm law taelamun qadarh ezym"
  56,77,"'in hdha alquran aladhi nazal ealaa muhamad laquran eazim almnafe, kthyr alkhyr, ghzyr alelm, fi kitab masun mstwr ean 'aeyun alkhlq, wahu alkitab aldhy bi'aydi almlayk. la yamass alquran 'iilaa almalayikat alkiram aladhin thrhm allah min alafat waldhnwb, wala yamassuh aydana 'iilaa almtthrwn min alshirk waljnabt walhdth"
  56,78,"'in hdha alquran aladhi nazal ealaa muhamad laquran eazim almnafe, kthyr alkhyr, ghzyr alelm, fi kitab masun mstwr ean 'aeyun alkhlq, wahu alkitab aldhy bi'aydi almlayk. la yamass alquran 'iilaa almalayikat alkiram aladhin thrhm allah min alafat waldhnwb, wala yamassuh aydana 'iilaa almtthrwn min alshirk waljnabt walhdth"
  56,79,"'iina hdha alquran aladhi nazal ealaa muhamad laquran eazim almnafe, kthyr alkhyr, ghzyr alelm, fi kitab masun mstwr ean 'aeyun alkhlq, wahu alkitab aldhy bi'aydi almlayk. la yamass alquran 'iilaa almalayikat alkiram aladhin thrhm allah min alafat waldhnwb, wala yamassuh aydana 'iilaa almtthrwn min alshirk waljnabt walhdth"
  56,80,"whdha alquran alkarim munazal min rabi alealmyn, fahu alhaqu aldhy la miryat fyh"
  56,81,afbhdha alquran 'antum -ayha almshrkwn- mkdhdhibwn?
  56,82,wtjelwn shkrkm lnem allah ealaykum 'anakum tkdhdhibwn biha wtkfrwn? wafi hdha 'inkar ealaa min ythawn bi'amr alquran wala ybaly bdewth
  56,83,"fhl tastatieun 'iidha balaghat nfs 'ahadakum alhulqum eind alnze, wa'antum hudur tunzirun 'ilyh, 'ana tumsikuu ruwhih fi jsdh? ln tastatieuu dhlk, wanahn 'aqrab 'iilayh minkum bmlayktna, wlknkm la trwnhm"
  56,84,"fhl tastatieun 'iidha balaghat nfs 'ahadakum alhulqum eind alnze, wa'antum hudur tunzirun 'ilyh, 'ana tumsikuu ruwhih fi jsdh? ln tastatieuu dhlk, wanahn 'aqrab 'iilayh minkum bmlayktna, wlknkm la trwnhm"
  56,85,"fhl tastatieun 'iidha balaghat nfs 'ahadakum alhulqum eind alnze, wa'antum hudur tunzirun 'ilyh, 'ana tumsikuu ruwhih fi jsdh? ln tastatieuu dhlk, wanahn 'aqrab 'iilayh minkum bmlayktna, wlknkm la trwnhm"
  56,86,"whl tastatieun 'iin kuntum ghayr mhasbyn wala mjzyyn baemalkm 'ana teydu alruwh 'iilaa aljsd, 'iin kuntum sadqyn? ln trjewha"
  56,87,"whl tastatieun 'iin kuntum ghayr mhasbyn wala mjzyyn baemalkm 'ana teydu alruwh 'iilaa aljsd, 'iin kuntum sadqyn? ln trjewha"
  56,88,"fama 'iin kan almayit min alssabiqin almqrbyn, falah eind mawtih alrahmat alwasieat walfrh wama ttyb bih nfsh, walah janat alnaeim fi alakhrt"
  56,89,"fama 'iin kan almayit min alssabiqin almqrbyn, falah eind mawtih alrahmat alwasieat walfrh wama ttyb bih nfsh, walah janat alnaeim fi alakhrt"
  56,90,"wa'amaa 'iin kan almayit min 'ashab alymyn, fyqal lh: salamat lak wamn; lkwnk min 'ashab alymyn"
  56,91,"wama 'iin kan almayit min 'ashab alymyn, fyqal lh: salamat lak wamn; lkwnk min 'ashab alymyn"
  56,92,"wama 'iin kan almayit min almukadhibin balbeth, aldaaliyn ean alhda, falah dyaft min sharab jahanam almghly almtnahy alhrart, walnaar yhrq bha, wayuqasi eadhabiha alshdyd"
  56,93,"wama 'iin kan almayit min almukadhibin balbeth, aldaaliyn ean alhda, falah dyaft min sharab jahanam almghly almtnahy alhrart, walnaar yhrq bha, wayuqasi eadhabiha alshdyd"
  56,94,"wama 'iin kan almayit min almukadhibin balbeth, aldaaliyn ean alhda, falah dyaft min sharab jahanam almghly almtnahy alhrart, walnaar yhrq bha, wayuqasi eadhabiha alshdyd"
  56,95,"'in hdha aldhy qssnah ealayk -ayha alrswl- lahu haqu alyaqin aldhy la miryat fyh, fsbbih biasm rabik alezym, wnzzihh eamaa yaqul alzaalimun waljahdwn, taealaa allah eamaa yaqulun elwana kbyrana"
  56,96,"'in hdha aldhy qssnah ealayk -ayha alrswl- lahu haqu alyaqin aldhy la miryat fyh, fsbbih biasm rabik alezym, wnzzihh eamaa yaqul alzaalimun waljahdwn, taealaa allah eamaa yaqulun elwana kbyrana"